Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Mystery Moon in the Night Sky!?\NAbove Ohtsuna City, right beside the actual moon, there is another\Nmoon-like thing floating in the night sky. It radiates light just like\Nthe real moon, but it is a different color. A meteorological research\Nagency was unable to detect that anything is really there.\NWhat the hell is this? The agency will use any means possible to\Ndetermine what this is, in cooperation with other nations...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that thing after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.98,0:00:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got potential.\NDon't you think, Chiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems that his powers have\Nnot been completely revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?\NShould we give him a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Test?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it on campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that thing\Nthat came after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on in this city?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that woman just an illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Square of the Moon:{\i0}\N{\i1}The Night Is Coming!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gently embraces us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without averting its eyes\Nin this endless night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blocking the light that turns pale
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stopping the flow of time\Nbrimming with lies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The naked words that were\Nthrown at the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to gather them\Nand vindicate them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness cannot happen unless\Nyou decide to go after it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The repeated days of giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go after you\Nmore than ever
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not sadness but\Nlove and courage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a flame hints at\Nthe beginning of life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give a reason for minor offense
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hell... two moons and wound
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sudden gust of wind\Npoints the path to the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hell to sea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gently embraces us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without averting its eyes\Nin this endless night
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:04:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing the souls that turn pale
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up from the sleep\Nbrimming with lies
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Square of the Moon:{\i0}\N{\i1}The Night Is Coming!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for the blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for the blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for the blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A train is arriving on Platform 3...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please stand behind the white line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're Ryo Hamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me at 8 PM on the\Nrooftop of Building #2.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up!\NWhat do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow! Don't be so rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she put you up to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sorry about that, Ryo Hamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wanted to test your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Power? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your reflexes that helped you\Ndodge those street signs yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the speed with which\Nyou were able to avoid my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're using a power that\Nyou're not even aware of yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A power just like ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday? You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you guys\Ngoing on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just bring him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo Hamura, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the head of the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're asking you to fight with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:05:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with these guys?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Astronomy Club{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't really understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all in the Astronomy\NClub, but that's just a cover...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're actually a\Nband of warriors called "The Kasha."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You come from that blue moon\Nup there and you fight monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like the one last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never met anyone who\Nunderstood her explanation in one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terrible at explaining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Ryo...\NHow about another cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot here, and I\Njust don't know what it all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can you give us an\Nanswer within a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really don't want anything\Nto do with what we talked about...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to have to\Nerase your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erase my memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you ugly nerd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. Why let it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's creepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what am I going to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That guy doesn't deserve a lover.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I'll just break them up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:07:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This rain sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear about the hottie\Nwho gets off in the park?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Eri!\NEnough with your text messaging!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gotoh, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Ryo? It's Izumi Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have time to think\Nabout what we talked about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I haven't decided anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you think you can make\Nit to Tamago Park tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to see for yourself\Nwhat a Light Hunter is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been coming here for\Nthe past two or three nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Light Hunters\Nprey on their victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Light Hunter is drawn to the\Nunfulfilled desires of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they live off of that energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we get that Light\NHunter off of her soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that woman will continue to\Nsee the dreams that it projects.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually she will become\Ntoo exhausted and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please. Fight with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. But how am I\Nsupposed to fight a monster like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll need some training in\Norder to use your power...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but let's do it together tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ancient fire. Your power\Nthat banishes the filth like the wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become a sword to this Kasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi! Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it just in time, Chiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kyoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sensed danger in the air\Naround this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought I'd\Ncheck it out just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Do you believe it now?\NWhat we were telling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please. Fight with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ancient fire. Mend the\Npain of this woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean her horrible\Nmemories will disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is all that we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm saying is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see the motive\Nbehind all these arson cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The arson cases continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A game arcade burns to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it caused by an angry\Ntenant with financial trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boutique where the\Nfire started is a total loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we were to assume that\Nthe Light Hunters are behind all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:14:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as they're\Nfeeding off of human desires,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should be seeing some common\Nthreads in where these fires are set.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the police, they only\Nhit busy areas where people gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they can figure\Nout where they'll strike next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering that they are taking\Nextra precautions to prevent fires,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the fact that the damage is getting\Nworse and worse makes me suspicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I guess that the\NLight Hunters are behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how could we know the motive\Nof someone they've possessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only place they've announced\Nwhere a fire started is a boutique.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we were to accept that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the motives would be the grudges\Nthat people had against that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't just leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For every fire started by the\Npeople possessed by Light Hunters,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there's got to\Nbe a reason behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess we just need\Nmore information.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...\NWhere are Kyoka and Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure was a great movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so good, especially\Nafter Megat met Tiro the Mute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What part of this is{\i0}\N{\i1}information gathering?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The information\Ngathering begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did tell you that I have\Nthe power of "Satori," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satori people can read\Nthe minds of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when it's all crowded like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an amazing power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just with the fluctuations in words,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're able to make lovey-dovey\Ncouples get into fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but are you\NManami Miwasaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to join our group?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:16:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the process of\Ngoing after a serial arsonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These aren't normal arson cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can count on\Nyour power of words,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll be able\Nto track down the arsonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew I could do\Nsomething like that with my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed something as I\Nwalked past that boutique last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow, how pretty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman in red?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Manami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a meeting\Nwe've got to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear more\Nabout what you saw, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoka, about that woman\Ndressed in red...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boutique where\Nthe fire took place...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was where a lot of Goths\Nand witch types went.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I have this feeling that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the next one will be on\Nthe sixth floor of that same building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. If the Light Hunters\Nhave possessed a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it's possible she'd\Nbe after a boutique or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? What\Nare you doing here, Manami?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go after the arsonist, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to meet that Light\NHunter woman and talk to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, I've been\Nusing my power of words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for stupid, unimportant things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if this power of mine\Ncan be of some use...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. You can come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo, you'll be responsible\Nfor protecting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo! I want you to go\Nahead to the sixth floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think they'll be all right alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of words is a rare\Nand highly effective power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Ryo is quite capable as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, stop! Let me talk to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone possessed by a Light\NHunter was once a regular person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to use\Nthe power of words,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe you can snap\Nher out of her suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the others to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can't do this.\NMaybe it's too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were lonely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were betrayed{\i0}\N{\i1}by someone you loved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you abandoned{\i0}\N{\i1}yourself somewhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You ran away from{\i0}\N{\i1}everything, and lived all alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cold... I'm cold... I'm cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. How thoughtless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pretty. It's burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you be satisfied\Nonly by burning your past?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that give you satisfaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can burn all the places\Nof your past,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but your sad memories\Nwill never go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not strangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're not family!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is going to change\Nunless you're willing to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not everyone is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you've got to have more strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you can be stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this will go on forever\Nand nothing will change!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.69,0:21:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to this, Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:21:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.21,0:22:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.38,0:22:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.60,0:22:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ryo, I suppose I{\i0}\N{\i1}could've expected this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've done terrible{\i0}\N{\i1}things all the time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I deserve to be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ravaged even more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.14,0:22:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.19,0:22:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.32,0:22:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:22:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo... Manami...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.99,0:23:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! The door won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.83,0:23:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we're\Ngoing to be finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.30,0:23:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo... Manami...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.17,0:23:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're conscious. Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was possessed\Nby the Light Hunter,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was being punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.15,0:23:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was toying with people's\Nhearts with my power of words.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.62,0:23:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I was\Ngoing to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.82,0:23:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. You just take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.86,0:23:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raisen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.14,0:23:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:23:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:23:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.92,0:24:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.66,0:24:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makoto, you saved us. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have grown weak, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.56,0:24:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so hard on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.40,0:24:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.57,0:24:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Makoto Kedoin?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.70,0:24:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Izumi said, that\Nwas an amazing technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to save that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.84,0:24:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.41,0:24:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.21,0:24:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the last moments,\Nher face was at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.02,0:24:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that she recaptured\Nher soul at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.39,0:24:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A happier fate than continuing to\Nlive possessed by the Light Hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.76,0:24:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice to think that. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.90,0:24:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.16,0:24:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.08,0:24:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet again soon. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.72,0:25:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya later, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.85,0:27:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More! Fuck me harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.65,0:27:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More! Please, more!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.86,0:27:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.52,0:27:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Haiji! Bite it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.67,0:28:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was great, Haiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.37,0:28:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.25,0:28:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're boring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.02,0:28:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something\Nstirring inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.79,0:28:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next Episode{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.96,0:28:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode of\N{\i1}Square of the Moon{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.63,0:28:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Wicked Moon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.67,0:28:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch it for me!
